OL,3,CNuclear veteran who had 'no
OL,4,Cprotection' at atom bomb trials calls
OL,5,Cfor inquiry
OL,7,FKris Jepson spoke to Jack Taylor who
OL,8,Fis calling for a public inquiry into
OL,9,FCold War nuclear testing in Australia
OL,10,Fin 1957
OL,12,FA veteran from South Tyneside has
OL,13,Fcalled on the government to hold a
OL,14,Fpublic inquiry into allegations of a
OL,15,Fcover-up which withheld thousands of
OL,16,Fmedical records from former service
OL,17,Fpersonnel who attended nuclear testing
OL,18,F70 years ago.
