OL,3,CNuclear veteran who had 'no
OL,4,Cprotection' at atom bomb trials calls
OL,5,Cfor inquiry
OL,7,FHe told ITV News Tyne Tees: "We had to
OL,8,Fstand with our backs to the explosion
OL,9,Ffor the initial blast, because it
OL,10,Fcould blind you if you saw that.
OL,12,F"Then you could turn around and see
OL,13,Fthe mushroom cloud go up, and then you
OL,14,Fgot the heat blast, which was
OL,15,Ftremendous.
OL,17,F"I can only describe it as like
OL,18,Fstanding against an oven and somebody
OL,19,Fopening the oven door and you get the
OL,20,Fheat blast out.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/10
