OL,3,CNuclear veteran who had 'no
OL,4,Cprotection' at atom bomb trials calls
OL,5,Cfor inquiry
OL,7,F"I had no protection. Just shorts,
OL,8,Fshoes, sandals or whatever, and not
OL,9,Feven a shirt.
OL,11,FWhen he returned to the UK, his back
OL,12,Fand parts of his chest were covered in
OL,13,Fa rash. He has had various medical
OL,14,Fissues over his lifetime, but said he
OL,15,Fhas "no idea" if they are related to
OL,16,Fcontamination as he was "never given a
OL,17,Fmedical".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/10
