OL,3,CNuclear veteran who had 'no
OL,4,Cprotection' at atom bomb trials calls
OL,5,Cfor inquiry
OL,7,FHe added: "I mean in hindsight, when
OL,8,Fyou think about Chernobyl and that,
OL,9,Fplaces like that which were
OL,10,Fcontaminated, how do I know that where
OL,11,Fwe were wasn't contaminated?
OL,13,F"In terms of medicals, if you like, we
OL,14,Fnever had one. Not either going or
OL,15,Fcoming home.
OL,17,F"The geiger counters we had, nobody
OL,18,Fever checked them. Nobody ever cAme up
OL,19,Fand said 'I'll give you factor seven
OL,20,For something to put on your back, you
OL,21,Fknow, not even that."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/10
