OL,7,FMany of his peers had blood tests
OL,8,Fduring the trials, which they claim
OL,9,Fhave been withheld by government after
OL,10,Fgovernment and Jack has been
OL,11,Fcampaigning with them for a public
OL,12,Finquiry ever since.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/10
