OL,3,CNuclear veteran who had 'no
OL,4,Cprotection' at atom bomb trials calls
OL,5,Cfor inquiry
OL,7,FHis local MP, Emma Lewell-Buck, raised
OL,8,Fthe issue at Prime Minister's
OL,9,FQuestions on Wednesday 24 July, when
OL,10,Fshe said: "These national heroes
OL,11,Fdeserve full accountability and
OL,12,Fjustice. Will he therefore consider
OL,13,Fsupporting a special tribunal with
OL,14,Fstatutory powers on this 70-year-long
OL,15,Fscandal?"
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/10
