OL,3,CNuclear veteran who had 'no
OL,4,Cprotection' at atom bomb trials calls
OL,5,Cfor inquiry
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer responded: "It is
OL,8,Fright that, I think, nearly 5,000 have
OL,9,Fnow got their nuclear test medals in
OL,10,Frecognition of their service and that
OL,11,Fthe veterans have the right to apply
OL,12,Ffor no-fault compensation under the
OL,13,Fwar pension scheme.
OL,15,F"I will ensure that a meeting on this
OL,16,Fissue is arranged for her with the
OL,17,Frelevant minister."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/10
