OL,3,CNuclear veteran who had 'no
OL,4,Cprotection' at atom bomb trials calls
OL,5,Cfor inquiry
OL,7,FThe South Shields politician told ITV
OL,8,FNews: "They've (the nuclear veterans)
OL,9,Fhad rare cancers, tumours. Some of
OL,10,Ftheir children have, you know, it's
OL,11,Fbeing passed down through the
OL,12,Fgenerations, and they just want to
OL,13,Fknow the truth, I mean people are fed
OL,14,Fup, aren't they, of state and
OL,15,Finstitutional cover ups. People just
OL,16,Fneed to know the truth."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/10
