OL,3,CNuclear veteran who had 'no
OL,4,Cprotection' at atom bomb trials calls
OL,5,Cfor inquiry
OL,7,FThe UK is the last nuclear power to
OL,8,Finsist its weapons tests caused no
OL,9,Fharm. The US, Australia, New Zealand,
OL,10,FRussia, China and France all
OL,11,Fcompensate their veterans.
OL,13,FJack received his service medal in
OL,14,F2023, but he said it is not about the
OL,15,Fmedal or the compensation, but
OL,16,Ffighting for justice for his fellow
OL,17,Fnuclear veterans.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/10
